OL,6,FWe have argued before that proposed BBC
OL,7,Fcuts can sometimes seem like          
OL,8,Fnegotiating positions.                
OL,10,FIn the past, plans to axe services such
OL,11,Fas 6 Music and the Red Button text    
OL,12,Fservice were dropped or substantially 
OL,13,Fmodified.                             
OL,15,FSo is the proposal to merge the BBC   
OL,16,FNews Channel and BBC World News also a
OL,17,Fnegotiating position? Or is it the    
OL,18,FBBC's final word?                     
OL,20,FIt seems NUJ members at the BBC are   
OL,21,Fbecoming increasingly concerned.      
OL,3,CBBC News Channel/BBC World News merger
OL,4,Cplans: more information required      
