OL,6,FNaturally there will be a worry over  
OL,7,Fjobs. Staff are having to reapply for a
OL,8,Freduced number of positions. Naturally
OL,9,Fthere is a fear over redundancies.    
OL,11,FIt should be stressed that any        
OL,12,Fcompulsory redundancies would almost  
OL,13,Fcertainly lead to industrial action.  
OL,14,FThe NUJ is in a very strong position at
OL,15,Fthe BBC.                              
OL,17,FBut this is not simply a concern for  
OL,18,Findividuals or jobs.                  
OL,3,CBBC News Channel/BBC World News merger
OL,4,Cplans: more information required      
OL,22,                                   G2/8
