OL,6,FPerhaps the bigger concern to the wider
OL,7,Fpublic is over just what the new      
OL,8,Fchannel will be like in practice. Far 
OL,9,Ftoo little has been said.             
OL,11,FWe know it will simulcast the main BBC
OL,12,FOne news programmes and Nicky         
OL,13,FCampbell's morning show on 5 Live. But
OL,14,Fwhat will happen the rest of the time?
OL,16,FWorld news is very important to an    
OL,17,Forganisation like the BBC. But there is
OL,18,Fa difference between covering world   
OL,19,Fnews and making bulletins for an      
OL,20,Finternational audience.               
OL,3,CBBC News Channel/BBC World News merger
OL,4,Cplans: more information required      
