OL,6,FMany major stories within the UK  the
OL,7,Fweather, train strikes, major court   
OL,8,Fcases  are of limited international  
OL,9,Finterest.                             
OL,11,FWhat will the running orders on the new
OL,12,Fchannel be like? What will the split be
OL,13,Flike between UK and world news?       
OL,15,FWhat about the current news channel's 
OL,16,Fcommitment to stories from the nations
OL,17,Fand the English regions?              
OL,19,FWhat will be the threshold for offering
OL,20,Fcoverage of domestic breaking news?   
OL,3,CBBC News Channel/BBC World News merger
OL,4,Cplans: more information required      
