OL,6,FMuch more will need to be said and done
OL,7,Fto provide reassurances the UK licence
OL,8,Fpayer will come first  not the       
OL,9,Fcommercial audience of BBC World.     
OL,11,FBut there are some other facts to     
OL,12,Fcontemplate.                          
OL,14,FFirst, of course, there is the pressure
OL,15,Fon the BBC's income. If one service is
OL,16,Fspared the axe, more cuts will be     
OL,17,Fneeded elsewhere.                     
OL,3,CBBC News Channel/BBC World News merger
OL,4,Cplans: more information required      
