OL,6,FSecondly, the audience at any one time
OL,7,Ffor the news channel is modest compared
OL,8,Fto the numbers who watch the main BBC 
OL,9,FOne bulletins  even though the news  
OL,10,Fchannel beats Sky News by a significant
OL,11,Fmargin.                               
OL,13,FThirdly, online services are          
OL,14,Fincreasingly important. How many of us
OL,15,Ffind out about breaking stories from  
OL,16,FBBC News alerts on our phones? Can you
OL,17,Fargue that the days of linear 24 hour 
OL,18,Fnews channels are numbered?           
OL,3,CBBC News Channel/BBC World News merger
OL,4,Cplans: more information required      
