OL,6,FStill the debate on what happens to the
OL,7,Fnews channel should be an important   
OL,8,Fdebate to the public. It goes to the  
OL,9,Fheart of what the BBC is ultimately   
OL,10,Fabout.                                
OL,12,FDo you pay a licence fee for what,    
OL,13,Fsadly, is now a failing soap opera   
OL,14,Fbeaten decisively in the ratings by   
OL,15,Fit's much-loved ITV rivals?           
OL,17,FOr do you pay for some of the best    
OL,18,Fjournalism going? Something that is   
OL,19,Fmore important now than ever in an era
OL,20,Fof fake news.                         
OL,3,CBBC News Channel/BBC World News merger
OL,4,Cplans: more information required      
