OL,6,FOr perhaps you feel the BBC still needs
OL,7,Fto offer as wide a range of services as
OL,8,Fpossible  the only question is about 
OL,9,Fwhether a service is of high quality or
OL,10,Fas good as it could be?               
OL,12,FBut if you feel like that, then you   
OL,13,Falso need to be prepared to debate what
OL,14,Fthe level of the licence fee should be
OL,15,For contemplate potential alternatives.
OL,17,FNothing would be worse than seeing the
OL,18,FBBC become a marginalised,            
OL,19,Fcash-strapped niche broadcaster. But  
OL,20,Fwithout more money, are we now on that
OL,21,Fpath?                                 
